}

###


# @name listAllMovies
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies
Authorization: Bearer {{acessToken}}
###

# @name listOneMovie
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies/{{idMovie}}
Authorization: Bearer {{acessToken}}
###
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies/10
Authorization: Bearer {{acessToken}}

